1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=The Moment I Met You=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:15,000
=Episode 22=

3
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:19,037
(A Land Blessed with Talents)

4
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:21,879
Who's there?

5
00:00:24,879 --> 00:00:26,199
It's the middle of the night.

6
00:00:32,399 --> 00:00:33,759
Thank you for saving my life, miss.

7
00:00:35,280 --> 00:00:37,359
Slow down. There's plenty more.

8
00:00:39,075 --> 00:00:40,362
(Liu Jun, Wandering Martial Artist)

9
00:00:40,399 --> 00:00:41,640
You'll make yourself sick.

10
00:00:44,359 --> 00:00:45,439
Here, have some water.

11
00:00:47,640 --> 00:00:48,840
For those of us on the road,

12
00:00:49,100 --> 00:00:50,359
starving is just part of life.

13
00:00:51,159 --> 00:00:52,600
I'm grateful for your kindness.

14
00:00:53,000 --> 00:00:54,439
I won't forget this.

15
00:00:58,159 --> 00:00:59,719
I must look pathetic, miss.

16
00:01:01,920 --> 00:01:03,640
Do you starve like this often?

17
00:01:04,640 --> 00:01:05,319
Often enough.

18
00:01:10,439 --> 00:01:11,319
You have my gratitude.

19
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:12,799
I'll take my leave.

20
00:01:23,200 --> 00:01:24,319
If you're ever hungry again,

21
00:01:24,680 --> 00:01:25,480
come back here.

22
00:01:25,690 --> 00:01:26,599
You can eat your fill.

23
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:34,719
Even the back of his head is handsome.

24
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:39,079
Yu,

25
00:01:39,640 --> 00:01:40,680
have you made up your mind?

26
00:01:41,239 --> 00:01:42,680
No regrets?

27
00:01:43,079 --> 00:01:43,719
Father,

28
00:01:44,239 --> 00:01:45,400
marrying Yunchang

29
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:47,120
would be my greatest honor.

30
00:01:47,210 --> 00:01:48,200
I would never regret it.

31
00:01:49,799 --> 00:01:50,480
Sir,

32
00:01:51,079 --> 00:01:52,719
I hope you'll give us your blessing.

33
00:01:59,439 --> 00:02:00,280
Very well.

34
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:01,799
Start preparing the wedding.

35
00:02:02,400 --> 00:02:03,239
Thank you, Father.

36
00:02:12,759 --> 00:02:13,240
This one.

37
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:40,159
Drinking again?

38
00:02:42,919 --> 00:02:43,560
Wushuang?

39
00:02:45,479 --> 00:02:46,560
Now I don't stand a chance

40
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:48,639
to win over my goddess Yunchang.

41
00:02:49,159 --> 00:02:51,879
Master is going to marry her.

42
00:02:52,950 --> 00:02:54,711
Mao Jixian approved the marriage?

43
00:02:56,080 --> 00:02:56,840
It's true.

44
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:59,000
The entire office
received wedding candy.

45
00:03:01,280 --> 00:03:02,080
Here's some for you.

46
00:03:07,700 --> 00:03:09,625
(Gate Bureau Archives)

47
00:03:10,199 --> 00:03:11,680
Chu Yunchang...

48
00:03:16,560 --> 00:03:17,159
Wushuang.

49
00:03:17,639 --> 00:03:19,000
If it wasn't meant to be,

50
00:03:19,759 --> 00:03:21,199
don't go doing anything rash.

51
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:23,639
There are still
plenty of fish in the sea.

52
00:03:24,919 --> 00:03:26,479
You should move on.

53
00:03:30,890 --> 00:03:31,400
Wait for me.

54
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:32,919
Cut back on the drinking.

55
00:03:34,879 --> 00:03:35,599
Wushuang.

56
00:03:37,240 --> 00:03:37,919
(Liu's Wedding Shop)
Yu,

57
00:03:38,199 --> 00:03:39,479
I heard you're getting married.

58
00:03:39,840 --> 00:03:40,680
Congratulations.

59
00:03:42,879 --> 00:03:43,879
Wushuang, are you...

60
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:45,919
What?

61
00:03:46,319 --> 00:03:47,840
I know how to move on.

62
00:03:48,080 --> 00:03:49,840
I'm not one to be dramatic.

63
00:03:50,039 --> 00:03:51,479
Trinkets and charms for sale!

64
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:53,080
Yu.

65
00:03:53,680 --> 00:03:56,639
Let me know when the big day comes.

66
00:03:56,639 --> 00:03:59,360
I'll be there to crash the bridal suite!

67
00:04:00,080 --> 00:04:00,719
I'll be waiting.

68
00:04:03,639 --> 00:04:05,159
Are you really Wushuang?

69
00:04:07,599 --> 00:04:09,000
This is wild.

70
00:04:11,639 --> 00:04:12,719
Do you have a death wish?

71
00:04:21,319 --> 00:04:21,959
My dear.

72
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:24,439
There's something
I'd like to discuss with you.

73
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:27,279
You can just give me an order, dear.

74
00:04:27,439 --> 00:04:28,480
Why bother discussing it?

75
00:04:28,879 --> 00:04:29,759
I've been thinking.

76
00:04:30,040 --> 00:04:31,000
You were right.

77
00:04:31,319 --> 00:04:33,120
I shouldn't leave such a heavy burden

78
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:34,720
all on Chang's shoulders.

79
00:04:35,399 --> 00:04:37,920
So, I've decided that after she's married,

80
00:04:39,319 --> 00:04:41,639
she should hang up her sword and retire

81
00:04:42,319 --> 00:04:43,360
from the Martial World.

82
00:04:44,680 --> 00:04:45,920
I'm glad you're so open-minded.

83
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:48,560
I'll thank you on her behalf.

84
00:04:49,399 --> 00:04:50,337
It's just that...

85
00:04:51,310 --> 00:04:53,025
the Sacred Hand Sect
can't just fall apart.

86
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:54,600
Therefore...

87
00:04:56,879 --> 00:04:58,839
I was thinking I should probably

88
00:05:00,240 --> 00:05:01,720
take over as Sect Leader.

89
00:05:02,639 --> 00:05:03,560
You, the Sect Leader?

90
00:05:03,879 --> 00:05:05,480
What's the matter? Am I not qualified?

91
00:05:05,480 --> 00:05:06,360
No, it's not that.

92
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:08,639
Of course you're qualified.

93
00:05:09,560 --> 00:05:10,240
However...

94
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:12,800
If I take over the sect now,

95
00:05:13,079 --> 00:05:14,360
it'll be hard to command respect.

96
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:15,680
I need to find

97
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:16,800
the other Sacred Hand Token

98
00:05:16,800 --> 00:05:17,800
to secure our sect's

99
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:19,079
place in the Martial World.

100
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:22,600
I've decided
to spend the rest of my life

101
00:05:22,600 --> 00:05:24,360
searching for that gold Token.

102
00:05:25,639 --> 00:05:26,240
Alright.

103
00:05:27,439 --> 00:05:28,279
I understand.

104
00:05:31,399 --> 00:05:32,199
But my dear,

105
00:05:33,160 --> 00:05:34,120
this means

106
00:05:34,879 --> 00:05:36,560
we can't have children
for the time being.

107
00:05:37,519 --> 00:05:39,199
A child would only tie me down.

108
00:05:39,639 --> 00:05:41,000
I don't want that right now.

109
00:05:45,279 --> 00:05:46,160
As you wish.

110
00:05:50,300 --> 00:05:52,362
(Happiness)

111
00:05:56,210 --> 00:05:56,959
Does it look good?

112
00:05:57,439 --> 00:05:58,040
It looks great.

113
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:00,160
By the way, Chang,

114
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:02,319
let's get our outfits
custom-made at Ruihexiang.

115
00:06:02,319 --> 00:06:03,399
Whatever you decide.

116
00:06:04,079 --> 00:06:04,720
I had no idea

117
00:06:04,770 --> 00:06:06,560
there'd be so much to prepare
for a wedding.

118
00:06:08,560 --> 00:06:09,720
And your guest list too.

119
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:11,240
Don't forget to get that to me soon.

120
00:06:12,680 --> 00:06:14,600
My family is pretty small, actually.

121
00:06:14,800 --> 00:06:15,920
Just me, my aunt and uncle,

122
00:06:15,920 --> 00:06:16,839
and Zhizhi.

123
00:06:17,160 --> 00:06:18,480
What about that Jade...

124
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:24,079
Will the elderly guy

125
00:06:24,439 --> 00:06:25,240
be there?

126
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:27,720
I don't know.

127
00:06:28,439 --> 00:06:30,720
I doubt he'll show up.

128
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:32,920
No.

129
00:06:33,439 --> 00:06:34,560
What I mean is,

130
00:06:34,959 --> 00:06:36,160
since he is...

131
00:06:38,480 --> 00:06:41,319
There'll be
a lot of constables at the wedding.

132
00:06:41,839 --> 00:06:42,720
I'm afraid he...

133
00:06:42,959 --> 00:06:44,639
I know. I understand.

134
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:46,600
He...

135
00:06:47,560 --> 00:06:48,920
He probably won't be there.

136
00:06:56,439 --> 00:06:57,839
(It's my wedding.)

137
00:06:58,560 --> 00:07:00,959
(Of course
I'd want my father to be there.)

138
00:07:12,150 --> 00:07:13,240
I haven't seen you in days.

139
00:07:13,759 --> 00:07:15,279
How'd you get so badly hurt?

140
00:07:16,399 --> 00:07:18,160
What happened?

141
00:07:19,279 --> 00:07:20,279
I ran into some enemies.

142
00:07:20,879 --> 00:07:21,720
Enemies?

143
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:23,120
Tell me who they are.

144
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,120
I'll go after them.

145
00:07:24,360 --> 00:07:25,240
They're long gone.

146
00:07:26,160 --> 00:07:27,399
I know no one else in the city,

147
00:07:28,519 --> 00:07:29,639
so I have to come to you.

148
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:33,639
Don't say that.

149
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:35,000
The fact that you told me

150
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:37,000
means you don't see me as a stranger.

151
00:07:42,600 --> 00:07:43,240
Zhizhi.

152
00:07:44,759 --> 00:07:46,079
You're the most beautiful,

153
00:07:46,639 --> 00:07:48,959
kind-hearted woman I've ever met.

154
00:07:52,759 --> 00:07:54,079
Stop talking nonsense.

155
00:07:54,879 --> 00:07:55,759
I mean it.

156
00:07:56,759 --> 00:07:57,879
Don't be mad,

157
00:07:58,399 --> 00:07:59,360
but to be honest,

158
00:08:00,079 --> 00:08:01,240
it was love at first sight.

159
00:08:02,360 --> 00:08:03,959
What are you talking about?

160
00:08:05,000 --> 00:08:06,079
That's impossible.

161
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:09,600
It's true.

162
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:11,399
Ever since the day we met,

163
00:08:11,399 --> 00:08:12,880
you've been all I can think about.

164
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:19,279
Actually,
I think you're pretty great too.

165
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:24,519
But I'm just a penniless wanderer

166
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:25,879
who lives on the road.

167
00:08:26,759 --> 00:08:27,600
I'm just afraid

168
00:08:29,879 --> 00:08:30,839
you'd look down on me.

169
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:33,919
That's not true.

170
00:08:34,960 --> 00:08:36,000
Don't say that.

171
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:39,039
Zhizhi.

172
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:52,600
Sister, my dear sister.

173
00:08:52,600 --> 00:08:54,200
My most beautiful sister.

174
00:08:54,519 --> 00:08:55,639
Please, I'm begging you.

175
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:57,759
Just talk to the master and madam.

176
00:08:58,120 --> 00:09:00,440
Tell them to let Liu Jun stay.

177
00:09:01,120 --> 00:09:01,840
Zhizhi.

178
00:09:02,240 --> 00:09:03,279
You've lost your mind.

179
00:09:03,480 --> 00:09:05,080
You don't even know where he's from,

180
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:07,120
yet you're ready
to throw your life away for him.

181
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:10,240
We're all part of the Martial World.

182
00:09:10,399 --> 00:09:12,720
We're all in the same line of work.

183
00:09:13,320 --> 00:09:14,440
If all else fails,

184
00:09:15,080 --> 00:09:16,679
you could just let him join the sect.

185
00:09:21,639 --> 00:09:22,440
What sect?

186
00:09:22,440 --> 00:09:23,559
What are you talking about?

187
00:09:23,799 --> 00:09:25,360
Why be so secretive?

188
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:27,080
It's not like he's with the Gate Bureau.

189
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:30,039
Then, go talk to Auntie yourself.

190
00:09:30,360 --> 00:09:31,279
I've stepped down.

191
00:09:32,519 --> 00:09:34,720
But, that's for after the wedding.

192
00:09:35,039 --> 00:09:36,879
You're still the Sect Leader for now.

193
00:09:36,879 --> 00:09:38,000
One word from you,

194
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:39,440
and it's done.

195
00:09:42,159 --> 00:09:42,840
Sect Leader,

196
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:44,360
I'm begging you.

197
00:09:45,759 --> 00:09:46,399
Zhizhi.

198
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:48,000
The last thing I want to hear

199
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:49,799
is anything about the Martial World.

200
00:09:51,480 --> 00:09:52,840
I've hung up my sword.

201
00:09:53,240 --> 00:09:55,279
From now on,
take these matters to Auntie.

202
00:09:56,159 --> 00:09:58,399
Then, why do you all hate him so much?

203
00:09:58,399 --> 00:10:00,559
Because we don't know
anything about his past.

204
00:10:01,050 --> 00:10:02,809
Is it really about his past?

205
00:10:02,900 --> 00:10:04,120
No, you're just being selfish.

206
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:05,919
You never care about how I feel!

207
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:10,600
Jun, let's go.

208
00:10:13,720 --> 00:10:14,360
Zhizhi!

209
00:10:14,519 --> 00:10:15,360
Come back!

210
00:10:19,519 --> 00:10:21,240
Scented sachets and trinkets!

211
00:10:21,240 --> 00:10:22,120
Come take a look!

212
00:10:22,120 --> 00:10:24,080
They don't care
about my feelings at all.

213
00:10:24,120 --> 00:10:26,000
This is the first time
I've ever liked someone,

214
00:10:26,080 --> 00:10:27,320
and they're all against me.

215
00:10:27,639 --> 00:10:28,240
Zhizhi.

216
00:10:28,480 --> 00:10:30,279
Your Matriarch
and the Young Lady suspect me.

217
00:10:30,300 --> 00:10:31,790
I shouldn't put you in this position.

218
00:10:32,159 --> 00:10:33,080
I should just leave.

219
00:10:34,320 --> 00:10:35,120
Jun.

220
00:10:35,879 --> 00:10:37,200
Please, don't leave me.

221
00:10:37,200 --> 00:10:38,559
I don't want to be a burden to you.

222
00:10:41,720 --> 00:10:43,120
Well, we don't have to live

223
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:44,039
under her roof.

224
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:45,720
When I'm in a good mood,

225
00:10:45,919 --> 00:10:47,480
I'll act as her little sidekick.

226
00:10:47,679 --> 00:10:48,639
But if I'm not,

227
00:10:49,519 --> 00:10:52,200
no one on this earth can boss around

228
00:10:52,200 --> 00:10:54,039
Raojiang's top Poison Master.

229
00:10:55,159 --> 00:10:55,799
Jun.

230
00:10:55,960 --> 00:10:57,200
Come on. Let's rent a place.

231
00:11:00,159 --> 00:11:03,200
Murder! Help!

232
00:11:03,210 --> 00:11:04,279
Where is that coming from?

233
00:11:04,559 --> 00:11:05,519
I think it's just ahead.

234
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:06,440
Let's go.

235
00:11:06,919 --> 00:11:08,240
Help! Murder!

236
00:11:08,759 --> 00:11:11,919
He's going to kill me! Help!

237
00:11:15,159 --> 00:11:15,919
Who are you?

238
00:11:15,919 --> 00:11:16,519
Get him!

239
00:11:44,720 --> 00:11:46,080
This thug who's appeared recently

240
00:11:46,320 --> 00:11:47,519
calls himself "Liu San the Bandit".

241
00:11:48,240 --> 00:11:49,159
Every time he strikes,

242
00:11:49,520 --> 00:11:51,399
he forces the victims
to call the authorities.

243
00:11:51,720 --> 00:11:53,759
He's luring the Gate Bureau officers
into a trap.

244
00:11:54,120 --> 00:11:55,240
He's quite a skilled fighter.

245
00:11:55,519 --> 00:11:57,200
It's like he's got a vendetta against us.

246
00:11:57,840 --> 00:11:58,919
The moment our men arrive,

247
00:11:59,120 --> 00:12:00,240
he cuts a few of them down

248
00:12:00,399 --> 00:12:01,240
and then escapes.

249
00:12:01,519 --> 00:12:02,759
Utterly arrogant!

250
00:12:04,200 --> 00:12:06,080
This is a direct insult
to the Gate Bureau.

251
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:08,120
Within three days,

252
00:12:08,360 --> 00:12:09,759
we'll have this Liu San

253
00:12:09,759 --> 00:12:11,720
standing trial in our hall.

254
00:12:12,190 --> 00:12:13,290
- Understood!
- Understood!

255
00:12:16,399 --> 00:12:17,200
Commissioner.

256
00:12:17,840 --> 00:12:19,360
Buyu's getting married in a few days.

257
00:12:19,639 --> 00:12:21,840
Shouldn't he stay out of this case?

258
00:12:22,570 --> 00:12:23,919
Director Liu, what are you saying?

259
00:12:24,360 --> 00:12:25,279
As a constable,

260
00:12:25,279 --> 00:12:26,799
I can't just sit by while he runs wild.

261
00:12:27,399 --> 00:12:29,840
I, Mao Buyu,
swear I'll capture this Liu San.

262
00:12:31,080 --> 00:12:32,360
Good. That's what I like to hear.

263
00:12:37,399 --> 00:12:39,200
He's openly flouting the law

264
00:12:39,679 --> 00:12:41,480
and has the nerve to taunt the Bureau.

265
00:12:41,919 --> 00:12:43,480
I can't let him get away with it.

266
00:12:44,679 --> 00:12:46,159
Every time he commits a crime,

267
00:12:46,440 --> 00:12:47,919
he makes sure to hurt your officers.

268
00:12:48,440 --> 00:12:50,080
He's clearly venting a personal grudge.

269
00:12:50,960 --> 00:12:52,200
I don't want you to get hurt.

270
00:12:53,039 --> 00:12:54,000
Don't worry, Chang.

271
00:12:54,720 --> 00:12:56,440
He's just a petty thief.

272
00:12:56,440 --> 00:12:57,799
I don't even care about him.

273
00:12:58,799 --> 00:13:00,279
Every time you went out on a case,

274
00:13:00,559 --> 00:13:01,960
did I ever try to stop you?

275
00:13:02,559 --> 00:13:04,039
I just don't know why,

276
00:13:04,240 --> 00:13:06,120
but I've got a bad feeling this time.

277
00:13:06,512 --> 00:13:08,193
Chang, you're just too nervous.

278
00:13:08,360 --> 00:13:09,200
Trust me.

279
00:13:09,759 --> 00:13:10,799
Within three days,

280
00:13:11,039 --> 00:13:13,679
I'll bring this bandit to justice.

281
00:13:14,039 --> 00:13:14,799
Fine.

282
00:13:15,559 --> 00:13:16,360
From now on,

283
00:13:16,679 --> 00:13:18,000
I'm staying here with the Yunchang

284
00:13:18,120 --> 00:13:18,960
to protect her.

285
00:13:24,720 --> 00:13:26,919
Elder Liu, I'm counting
on you for everything.

286
00:13:27,399 --> 00:13:28,039
Don't worry.

287
00:13:28,039 --> 00:13:29,200
The Beggar Sect always helps

288
00:13:29,200 --> 00:13:30,639
with Sacred Hand Sect business.

289
00:13:30,639 --> 00:13:32,919
(She says she's done
with the Martial World.)

290
00:13:33,320 --> 00:13:34,720
(But now, for Mao Buyu,)

291
00:13:34,720 --> 00:13:36,680
(she's even using her ties
with the Beggar Sect.)

292
00:13:37,399 --> 00:13:38,720
(When her fiancé's in trouble,)

293
00:13:38,720 --> 00:13:39,720
(she goes all out to help.)

294
00:13:39,720 --> 00:13:40,320
Take care.

295
00:13:40,320 --> 00:13:42,399
(But when I begged her
to help the man I love,)

296
00:13:42,399 --> 00:13:43,900
(she just made all sorts of excuses.)

297
00:13:45,740 --> 00:13:46,480
(Double standards.)

298
00:13:52,080 --> 00:13:54,399
Don't you think
she has double standards?

299
00:13:54,720 --> 00:13:55,840
That's just how people are.

300
00:13:55,960 --> 00:13:58,159
They don't care unless it affects them.

301
00:14:01,080 --> 00:14:03,000
We grew up together

302
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:04,200
like sisters,

303
00:14:05,720 --> 00:14:07,200
yet she's treating me like this.

304
00:14:10,799 --> 00:14:12,159
Have you heard

305
00:14:12,440 --> 00:14:14,120
of this bandit, Liu San?

306
00:14:14,710 --> 00:14:16,392
I've traveled
the Martial World for years,

307
00:14:17,200 --> 00:14:18,480
but I've never heard that name.

308
00:14:19,399 --> 00:14:20,240
That makes sense.

309
00:14:20,600 --> 00:14:22,840
Even the Beggar Sect doesn't know him.

310
00:14:23,360 --> 00:14:25,480
Who exactly is this lady?

311
00:14:25,620 --> 00:14:27,240
Even the Beggar Sect does what she says.

312
00:14:28,180 --> 00:14:29,720
Have you heard of the Sacred Hand Sect?

313
00:14:32,679 --> 00:14:34,120
She's the Sect Leader.

314
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:40,240
I see. A powerful figure indeed.

315
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:45,919
Nothing found.

316
00:14:46,000 --> 00:14:46,720
That's right.

317
00:14:47,240 --> 00:14:49,960
I sent carrier pigeons
to all thirteen sub-branches,

318
00:14:49,960 --> 00:14:52,240
yet no one's heard of

319
00:14:52,320 --> 00:14:54,399
Liu San the Bandit.

320
00:14:54,679 --> 00:14:55,720
He appeared out of nowhere?

321
00:14:55,879 --> 00:14:56,480
This...

322
00:14:58,840 --> 00:14:59,399
Miss,

323
00:14:59,639 --> 00:15:00,759
a letter from Wu Buzhi.

324
00:15:07,125 --> 00:15:09,300
(I don't know him.)

325
00:15:09,770 --> 00:15:11,240
Even Wu Buzhi couldn't find anything.

326
00:15:13,050 --> 00:15:15,110
You want me to drop
the case of Liu San the Bandit?

327
00:15:15,799 --> 00:15:16,440
That's right.

328
00:15:16,620 --> 00:15:18,679
You should focus
on planning the wedding right now.

329
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:20,000
Don't touch this case.

330
00:15:20,279 --> 00:15:22,320
But solving a case won't
interfere with our wedding.

331
00:15:23,320 --> 00:15:24,799
I don't care.

332
00:15:25,279 --> 00:15:27,440
You have to focus
on the wedding right now.

333
00:15:27,720 --> 00:15:29,320
You don't have time for that case.

334
00:15:29,519 --> 00:15:30,799
Just listen to me for once.

335
00:15:33,320 --> 00:15:34,720
You used to support my work.

336
00:15:34,919 --> 00:15:36,440
Why are you being so unreasonable?

337
00:15:37,290 --> 00:15:38,639
I'll be as unreasonable as I want.

338
00:15:38,639 --> 00:15:40,480
If you don't listen to me,

339
00:15:40,480 --> 00:15:41,799
I'll make a scene at the office.

340
00:15:42,350 --> 00:15:43,480
I'll take it up with your Chief.

341
00:15:43,480 --> 00:15:44,080
Don't you dare.

342
00:15:46,240 --> 00:15:47,320
Did you just yell at me?

343
00:15:49,320 --> 00:15:50,519
As an officer of the law,

344
00:15:50,700 --> 00:15:51,799
I serve the Imperial Court.

345
00:15:51,799 --> 00:15:53,799
Investigating cases is my duty.

346
00:15:53,860 --> 00:15:55,720
I can't neglect my duty
for personal reasons.

347
00:15:57,919 --> 00:15:58,639
Fine.

348
00:15:59,039 --> 00:16:00,520
If you're going to work on this case,

349
00:16:00,879 --> 00:16:02,399
then the wedding's postponed.

350
00:16:04,440 --> 00:16:06,039
Fine. Have it your way.

351
00:16:06,240 --> 00:16:08,080
We'll plan the wedding after

352
00:16:08,080 --> 00:16:09,200
I catch Liu San the Bandit.

353
00:16:09,519 --> 00:16:11,000
Mao Buyu, how dare you?

354
00:16:11,360 --> 00:16:12,080
I said...

355
00:16:13,600 --> 00:16:14,559
It's settled then.

356
00:16:15,639 --> 00:16:16,679
Get back here!

357
00:16:19,919 --> 00:16:20,720
It's decided.

358
00:16:24,399 --> 00:16:25,159
(What should I do?)

359
00:16:25,400 --> 00:16:27,460
(I've never had
a premonition this strong before.)

360
00:16:27,960 --> 00:16:30,759
(There's definitely
more to this case than meets the eye.)

361
00:16:35,367 --> 00:16:38,642
♪Grudges and regrets
are like strong wine♪

362
00:16:38,680 --> 00:16:41,555
♪Drink it down and let it go♪

363
00:16:42,055 --> 00:16:47,773
♪An empty cup for our love and hate♪

364
00:16:48,955 --> 00:16:52,275
♪Tears blur a fate I can't control♪

365
00:16:52,405 --> 00:16:55,325
♪Let's drink until dawn♪

366
00:16:56,493 --> 00:17:01,733
♪Behind this mask, I'll never lie♪

367
00:17:02,955 --> 00:17:05,348
♪Every reunion feels like the first♪

368
00:17:05,348 --> 00:17:08,998
♪This hidden smile will never fade♪

369
00:17:09,067 --> 00:17:12,557
♪One heart, standing by your side♪

370
00:17:12,655 --> 00:17:15,630
♪To the ends of time♪

371
00:17:15,630 --> 00:17:19,005
♪The moon traces your face♪

372
00:17:19,192 --> 00:17:22,780
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

373
00:17:22,780 --> 00:17:29,020
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

374
00:17:29,355 --> 00:17:32,570
♪A silent prayer in my soul♪

375
00:17:32,855 --> 00:17:36,393
♪Carrying my vow beneath the moon♪

376
00:17:36,680 --> 00:17:39,705
♪Hoping we never drift apart again♪

377
00:17:39,705 --> 00:17:42,805
♪On our way to forever♪

378
00:17:42,805 --> 00:17:46,655
♪The moon traces your face♪

379
00:17:46,655 --> 00:17:50,015
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

380
00:17:50,205 --> 00:17:56,165
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

381
00:17:57,242 --> 00:18:06,882
♪Just to be with you♪
